   Sousa Torres, Jose Alberto; da Silva, Daniel Alves; Vergara, Guilherme Fay; Lopes Mendonca, Fabio Lucio; de Sousa Junior, Rafael Timoteo, Univ Brasilia UnB, Cyber Secur INCT Unit 6, Lab Decis Making Technol LATITUDE, Dept Elect Engn ENE,Fac Technol, Brasilia, DF, Brazil.
   dos Santos, Paulo Henrique; Lacerda Veiga, Carlos Eduardo; Medeiros, Marcio Bastos; Lopes Mendonca, Fabio Lucio, Advocacy Gen Union Brazil, Brasilia, DF, Brazil.},
DOI = {10.1109/ICDMW58026.2022.00022},
ISSN = {2375-9232},
